{"title":"01串","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1708","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给定7个整数N,A<sub>0</sub>,B<sub>0</sub>,L<sub>0</sub>,A<sub>1</sub>,B<sub>1</sub>,L<sub>1</sub>，要求设计一个01串S=s<sub>1</sub>s<sub>2</sub>…s<sub>i</sub>…s<sub>N</sub>，满足：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>s<sub>i</sub>=0或s<sub>i</sub>=1，1&lt;=i&lt;=N；</li>\n<li>对于S的任何连续的长度为L<sub>0</sub>的子串s<sub>j</sub>s<sub>j+1</sub>…s<sub>j+L0-1</sub>(1&lt;=j&lt;=N-L<sub>0</sub>+1)，0的个数大于等于A<sub>0</sub>且小于等于B<sub>0</sub>;</li>\n<li>对于S的任何连续的长度为L<sub>1</sub>的子串s<sub>j</sub>s<sub>j+1</sub>…s<sub>j+L1-1</sub>(1&lt;=j&lt;=N-L<sub>1</sub>+1)，1的个数大于等于A<sub>1</sub>且小于等于B<sub>1</sub>;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>例如，N=6,A<sub>0</sub>=1,B<sub>0</sub>=2,L<sub>0</sub>=3,A<sub>1</sub>=1,B<sub>1</sub>=1,L<sub>1</sub>=2，则存在一个满足上述所有条件的01串S=010101。</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\"><br></span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>仅一行，有<span>7</span>个整数，依次表示<span>N,A<sub>0</sub>,B<sub>0</sub>,L<sub>0</sub>,A<sub>1</sub>,B<sub>1</sub>,L<sub>1</sub></span>，相邻两个整数之间用一个空格分隔。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仅一行，若不存在满足所有条件的<span lang=\"EN-US\">01</span>串，则输出一个整数<span lang=\"EN-US\">-1</span>，否则输出一个满足所有条件的<span lang=\"EN-US\">01</span>串。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>6 1 2 3 1 1 2</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>010101</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>3&lt;=N&lt;=1000</span>，<span>1&lt;= A<sub>0</sub>&lt;=B<sub>0</sub>&lt;=L<sub>0</sub>&lt;=N</span>，<span>1&lt;=A<sub>1</sub>&lt;=B<sub>1</sub>&lt;=L<sub>1</sub>&lt;=N</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}